  "explanation": "<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Reč <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Salvadoreña</span> je ženski oblik nacionalnosti osobe iz El Salvadora.</p>\n<p>Imena moraju se slagati po rodu sa opisanošću osobom. Primer:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Pol</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Državljanstvo</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Primer</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><strong>Žensko</strong></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Salvadoreña</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Ella es salvadoreña.</span> (\"Yeye ni Msalvadorian\".)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><strong>Muško</strong></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Salvadoreño</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Él es salvadoreño.</span> (\"Yeye ni Msalvadorian\".)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>",
